quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,"Ègbé ni fún gbogbo abúnilójú-ẹni, abúnilẹ́yìn-ẹni"
  104,2,"ẹni tí ó kó owó jọ, tí ó sì kà á lákàtúnkà (láì ná an fẹ́sìn)"
  104,3,Ó ń lérò pé dájúdájú dúkìá rẹ̀ yóò mú un ṣe gbére (nílé ayé)
  104,4,Rárá (kò rí bẹ́ẹ̀). Dájúdájú wọ́n máa kù ú lókò sínú Hutọmọh ni
  104,5,Kí sì ni ó mú ọ mọ ohun t’ó ń jẹ́ Hutọmọh
  104,6,(Òhun ni) Iná Allāhu tí wọ́n ń kò (t’ó ń jò geregere)
  104,7,èyí tí ó máa jó (ẹ̀dá) wọ inú ọkàn lọ
  104,8,Dájúdájú wọ́n máa ti (àwọn ìlẹ̀kùn) Iná pa mọ́ wọn lórí pátápátá
  104,9,(Wọ́n máa wà) láààrin àwọn òpó kìrìbìtì gíga (nínú Iná)